\f0\fs24 \cf0 Frankenstein seems like an old horror story about a guy who makes a monster from a bunch of body parts. In fact, Victor Frankenstein, the modern Prometheus, is about the birth of the still living thing modern AI, how companies like Open AI are now racing to create the most powerful AI, ChatGPT, and how Victor Frankenstein and AI developers are scared of the consequences of playing God. Victor Frankenstein is obsessed with his experiments. He doesn't create life to help humanity. He does it because he can. Unlike Victor, AI tech creators are obsessed with tech, and Victor Frankenstein obsessed with humanity. There is a thin line AI creators and Victor Frankenstein are playing with. In a world of no limits and no possible consequences. Victor sees his creation as a catastrophe because he is playing God, and like Victor, many creators see their creation in the same way. Many scientists warn us of a powerful AI. A catastrophe if there are no limits in place.\
